Project description

Ninja is a small build system with a focus on speed.

The latest Ninja python wheels provide ninja 1.11.1.g95dee.kitware.jobserver-1 executableand ninja_syntax.py for generating .ninja files.

History

ninja-python-distributions was initially developed in November 2016 byJean-Christophe Fillion-Robin to facilitate the distribution of project usingscikit-build and depending on CMakeand Ninja.
